    JOZ  Jordan, Middle East.
    LBZ  Lebanon, Middle East.
    ILZ  Israel, Middle East.
    SYZ  Syria, Middle East.
    EGZ  Egypt, Africa.
    QRZ  European Economic Community (EC).
