<HEADLINE>
FT  18 OCT 94 / London Stock Exchange: Eurotunnel down
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By STEVE THOMPSON, PETER JOHN and JEFFREY BROWN
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Eurotunnel's announcement that revenue for 1994 would be in the region of
Pounds 34m, and not the Pounds 137m forecast at the time of the May rights
